title: Seeing Yourself As A Masterpiece | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Seeing Yourself As A Masterpiece | Joel Osteen
description:
f you’re going to reach your highest potential, you have to see yourself as God's masterpiece. Nothing about you is an accident. You were carefully designed with everything you need to fulfill your destiny. 


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
